<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/103000868/2025-26/evaluation> a ns1:EvaluationSystem ;
    ns1:evaluationDescription """This course is intended to be practical. iIt is encouraged that pupils bring their own laptop to follow laboratory classes.
In this subject a progressive evaluation is carried out, the 'Daily work assignment', with a weight of 10% of the subject will not be recoverable in the global evaluation, since it evaluates the daily work of the students. This test will be done in class and in a maximum of two deliveries. It is not recoverable in the ordinary call, nor in the extraordinary since it is used as a control and consolidation mechanism of knowledge acquired by stidents and as a tool to re-adapt teaching based on its results.
All presentations and documents required in assignments should be written in English, as well as pupil's presentations."""@es .

